    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it's looking for a brand new home. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me! It\u2019s been well-cared for, runs like a dream, and is ready for many more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
