    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit boasts a broad powerband thanks to its high-revving individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system. The chassis has been properly sorted with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings throughout. Suspension is handled by a set of Bilstein B16 coilovers, ensuring precise damping and minimal body roll. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, making this a turn-key driver's car for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Interior is clean. Mechanically sound. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
