    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a great car. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver without the 'new car' price tag. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and it still drives like a dream! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to move!",
