    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical maintenance has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced with a weld-in plate kit, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals. The engine retains its 8,000 RPM redline with excellent compression across all six cylinders. Handling is sharpened via a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers and reinforced RTABs. While the Titanium Silver finish shows minor road-going patina, the chassis dynamics and powertrain remains optimized for technical driving.",
